OL,3,CVeteran radio star Johnnie Walker dies
OL,4,Caged 79
OL,6,FHis wife Tiggy said: "I couldn't be
OL,7,Fmore proud of Johnnie - how he kept
OL,8,Fbroadcasting almost to the end and
OL,9,Fwith what dignity and grace he coped
OL,10,Fwith his debilitating lung disease.
OL,12,F"He remained his charming, humorous
OL,13,Fself to the end, what a strong,
OL,14,Famazing man. It has been a
OL,15,Frollercoaster ride from start to
OL,16,Ffinish.
