OL,6,F"And if I may say - what a day to go.
OL,7,FHe'll be celebrating New Year's Eve
OL,8,Fwith a stash of great musicians in
OL,9,Fheaven. One year on from his last live
OL,10,Fshow.
OL,12,F"God bless that extraordinary husband
OL,13,Fof mine, who is now in a place of
OL,14,Fpeace."
OL,16,FWalker had announced in early October
OL,17,Fhe was retiring from radio after 58
OL,18,Fyears, having previously been
OL,19,Fdiagnosed with idiopathic pulmonary
OL,20,Ffibrosis (IPF).
