OL,6,FThe terminal condition causes the
OL,7,Flungs to become scarred and makes
OL,8,Fbreathing increasingly more difficult.
OL,10,FHe presented his final Sounds Of The
OL,11,F70s show on BBC Radio 2 and hosted his
OL,12,Flast episode of The Rock Show at the
OL,13,Fend of October.
OL,15,FThe BBC's director general, Tim Davie,
OL,16,Fsaid: "We are deeply saddened by the
OL,17,Fnews of Johnnie's passing and our
OL,18,Fthoughts are with his family and
OL,19,Ffriends, as well as everyone at Radio
OL,20,F2.
