OL,6,F"Johnnie was a pop radio pioneer and a
OL,7,Fchampion of great music, entertaining
OL,8,Fmillions of beloved listeners on the
OL,9,FBBC across decades, most recently
OL,10,Fhosting two shows on Radio 2.
OL,12,F"No one loved the audience as much as
OL,13,FJohnnie and we loved him back."
OL,15,FWalker left school at the age of 15 to
OL,16,Ftrain to become a mechanic, later
OL,17,Ftaking a job as a car salesman.
OL,19,FWalker began his radio career in 1966
OL,20,Fon Swinging Radio England, an offshore
OL,21,Fpirate station.
