OL,6,FWalker would go on to join BBC Radio 1
OL,7,Fin 1969, continuing until 1976, with
OL,8,Fhim later moving to San Francisco,
OL,9,Fwhere he recorded a weekly show
OL,10,Fbroadcast on Radio Luxembourg.
OL,12,FHe returned to the UK in the 80s and
OL,13,Fpresented Radio 1's Saturday Stereo
OL,14,FSequence.
OL,16,FAfter working on various BBC stations,
OL,17,Fhe left Radio 1 for good in 1995 and
OL,18,Fthree years later he was offered his
OL,19,Fown weekly show on Radio 2, before
OL,20,Ftaking over Drivetime.
