OL,11,FHe earned a reputation as a DJ who
OL,12,Faccorded more importance to the
OL,13,Frecords he played than the chat
OL,14,Fbetween tracks, with names he
OL,15,Fpioneered including Lou Reed,
OL,16,FFleetwood Mac and The Eagles.
OL,18,FIn October 2003, Walker underwent
OL,19,Fchemotherapy and an emergency
OL,20,Foperation for non-Hodgkin's lymphoma.
