OL,6,FHe told his listeners live on air of
OL,7,Fthe diagnosis and later revealed that
OL,8,Fhe "died" on the operating table three
OL,9,Ftimes during surgery to repair his
OL,10,Fburst intestine.
OL,12,FIn 2019, he underwent surgery for
OL,13,Fheart problems later saying that he
OL,14,Fsuffered a heart attack and needed a
OL,15,Ftriple heart bypass.
OL,17,FWalker had to use an oxygen machine
OL,18,Ffor his IPS and was wheelchair-bound
OL,19,Ftowards the end of his life.
